metadata.name: The Lounge
metadata.description:
The Lounge, HAYA and Aged Spirits

HANI HAYA
worked in 2022

2329 × 3963pixel, 300DPI
PNG

The Malt Lounge, collected malts all gives satisfaction and feel more full even just looking it.
Chose the fine one, pour into a glass, and swirl the glass.
Make nose running into it and say "Hello", "How're you" then whisky says "Quite well".
And put it on mouth, silky, fruity, less of kick, strong green apple flavor all through in time.
Swallow it and let the breathe out, this is the malt lounge.

This NFT piece including a 2.5D aluminum art panel, with produced by GASHO 2.0, the highest bidder will receive the art panel.
